title: Sobriety, Mental Health, and Insta Archiving
description:
Lala and Rand set the record straight about their relationship, rumored weekend breakup, and Insta archiving! Lala also speaks to mental health, sobriety, the 12 steps, and her own daily struggle. Plus, Lala and Rand answer a few of your voicemails!
